BBC web-site Login: failPath test case

Preconditions:
1. The user was created with the next credentials:
Login: stanfortest@mail.ru
Password: Password@Test

Steps:
1. Open https://www.bbc.com/
2. Click on "Sign in" button
3. Fill in the "Login" input field with "stanfortest@mail.ru"
4. Fill in the "Password" input field with "!@#$%^&*()"
5. Click on the confirmation button

Expected Result:
1. https://www.bbc.com/ web-site was opened
2. The page with "Sign in" form was opened
3. The "Login" input field was filled with "stanfortest@mail.ru"
4. 3. The "Password" input field was filled with "!@#$%^&*()"
5. The user was not logged in. "Извините, этот пароль недействителен" error message is displayed